panels.title: Size, color mapped to different fields + share view
Extracting individual values
panels.description: Some data sources (for example MQTT) might be consuming incomparable metrics packaged in the same JSON payload. We can use this extract fields transformation's JSON option to select the specific fields we want, and alias the values to help classify unlabeled or unstructured data.
